":"Margit was born in 1410, in Turku, Turku ja Pori, Finland. She married Mattis Skalenberg in 1432, in Turku, Turku ja Pori, Finland. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died in 1465, in her hometown, at the age of 55."},"et":{"1410–1465":"1410–1465","1390–1460":"1390–1460","–1460":"–1460","1430–1475":"1430–1475","1432–1472":"1432–1472","1410":"1410","1432":"1432","1465":"1465","1475":"1475","1430":"1430","after 1460":"pärast 1460","1472":"1472","1460":"1460","1390":"1390","Hvills, Turku, Pori, Finland":"Turku, Turku ja Pori, Soome","Hvittis, Turku Pori, Finland":"Turku, Turku ja Pori, Soome","Hvittis, Turku, Pori, Finland":"Turku, Turku ja Pori, Soome","Sweden":"Rootsi","Sjötorp,Hallarne Broddarp, Västergötland/ Älvsborgs Län, Sverige":"Broddarp, Älvsborg, Rootsi","Pori, Turku ja Pori, Finland":"Pori, Soome"},"fi":{"1410–1465":"1410–1465","1390–1460":"1390–1460","–1460":"–1460","1430–1475":"1430–1475","1432–1472":"1432–1472","1410":"1410","1432":"1432","1465":"1465","1475":"1475","1430":"1430","after 1460":"1460 jälkeen","1472":"1472","1460":"1460","1390":"1390","Hvills, Turku, Pori, Finland":"Turku, Turku ja Pori, Suomi","Hvittis, Turku Pori, Finland":"Turku, Turku ja Pori, Suomi","Hvittis, Turku, Pori, Finland":"Turku, Turku ja Pori, Suomi","Sweden":"Ruotsi","Sjötorp,Hallarne Broddarp, Västergötland/ Älvsborgs Län, Sverige":"Broddarp, Älvsborg, Ruotsi","Pori, Turku ja Pori, Finland":"Pori, Suomi"},"fr":{"1410–1465":"1410–1465","1390–1460":"1390–1460","–1460":"–1460","1430–1475":"1430–1475","1432–1472":"1432–1472","1410":"1410","1432":"1432","1465":"1465","1475":"1475","1430":"1430","after 1460":"après 1460","1472":"1472","1460":"1460","1390":"1390","Hvills, Turku, Pori, Finland":"Turku, Turku ja Pori, Finlande","Hvittis, Turku Pori, Finland":"Turku, Turku ja Pori, Finlande","Hvittis, Turku, Pori, Finland":"Turku, Turku ja Pori, Finlande","Sweden":"Suède","Sjötorp,Hallarne Broddarp, Västergötland/ Älvsborgs Län, Sverige":"Broddarp, Älvsborg, Suède",